==抽签仪式==
2020年夏季奥林匹克运动会男子足球赛的抽签分组仪式将在2021年4月21日上午10时([[UTC+02:00|UTC+2]])举行，地点在位于[[瑞士|瑞士]][[苏黎世|苏黎世]]的[[国际足联总部|国际足联总部]]举行<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.fifa.com/mensolympic/news/tokyo-2020-olympic-draws-to-be-held-at-the-home-of-fifa|title=Tokyo 2020 Olympic draws to be held at the Home of FIFA|work=FIFA|date=22 March 2021|accessdate=22 March 2021|archive-date=2021-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322084359/https://www.fifa.com/mensolympic/news/tokyo-2020-olympic-draws-to-be-held-at-the-home-of-fifa}}</ref>。该抽签仪式由国际足联首席女子足球官员{{tsl|en|Sarai Bareman|萨拉伊·巴雷曼}}和国际足联赛事总监Jaime Yarza主持。

这16支参赛球队被分为4组，每组4支球队。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.fifa.com/womensolympic/news/draws-set-path-to-tokyo-2020-gold |title=Draws set path to Tokyo 2020 gold |work=FIFA |date=21 April 2021 |access-date=21 April 2021 |archive-date=2021-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516113145/https://www.fifa.com/womensolympic/news/draws-set-path-to-tokyo-2020-gold }}</ref>[[日本|日本]]以东道主的身份自动被送入第一档次并成为A1队，而其余球队则根据最近五届奥运会（最近的比赛比重得更大）的结果而被排入各自的档次，并为联盟冠军奖励积分。每个组不会有超过一个来自同一个大洲的球队。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://img.fifa.com/image/upload/bvr7nplx6nb8jhqjxjp0.pdf|title=Draw Procedures – Olympic Football Tournaments Tokyo 2020 – Men's tournament|format=PDF|work=FIFA|access-date=2021-04-22|archive-date=2021-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210323181503/https://img.fifa.com/image/upload/bvr7nplx6nb8jhqjxjp0.pdf}}</ref>

